       ["itertools"],
       true,
       "itertools.repeat.__module__.__eq__('itertools') == True — repeat is a C extension type in itertoolsmodule.c; its __module__ attribute is 'itertools' reflecting the module it is declared in; str.__eq__('itertools') returns True; new to extra159"]

